<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Allett Turfcare Equipment</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/allet.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Stylesheets/footer.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('Layoutsheets/navbar.ejs') %>
    <section class="intro">
        <div class="title"><div class="chn"><img src="../images/al0.jpeg" class="chn" /></div>
            <div class="ch"><h2 class="texttit">Allett Turfcare Equipment</h2>
                <div class="allett-info">
                    <p>Allett cylinder mowers deliver a flawless cut, ensuring a healthy, vibrant lawn every time. Designed for all lawn sizes—from small gardens to professional sports fields—these mowers are built for durability and ease of use.</p>
                    <h3>Why Choose Allett?</h3>
                    <ul>
                      <li><strong>Precision Blades</strong>: Perfect cuts for lush, healthy grass.</li>
                      <li><strong>Versatile</strong>: Ideal for all lawn sizes, from home gardens to sports grounds.</li>
                      <li><strong>Durable</strong>: Long-lasting, reliable performance.</li>
                      <li><strong>Effortless Use</strong>: Easy to operate for fast, efficient mowing.</li>
                      <li><strong>Eco-Friendly</strong>: Battery-powered options for a greener choice.</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>     
    </div>
    </section>

    <section class="allett-range">
        <div class="section-title">Homeowner Range</div>
        <p class="section-description">ALLETT produces the widest range of walk-behind cylinder mowers for home garden lawns. Designed for medium to large lawns, these mowers guarantee a precise cut every time.</p>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al1.jpg" alt="Allett Stirling" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Stirling Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">Battery-electric mowers offering exact, robust mowing with a cartridge system for professional-level lawn-thatch control, autumn renovations, and weed control. Designed for medium to large lawns, the Stirling range provides a perfect blend of precision, ease of use, and eco-friendly operation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al2.jpg" alt="Allett Liberty" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Liberty Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">Cordless lithium-ion battery-powered cylinder mowers, offering convenience and advanced mowing technology for the home lawn enthusiast. The Liberty range ensures effortless mowing with a clean, crisp finish on any lawn size, all while reducing environmental impact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al3.webp" alt="Allett Kensington" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Kensington Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">Petrol mowers available in 14", 17", and 20" cutting widths. Offers precision cutting and is built for a superior finish for lawn enthusiasts. With its robust engine and durable design, the Kensington is ideal for homeowners looking for a professional finish with minimal effort.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section-title">Sports & Pro Range</div>
        <p class="section-description">Professional-grade cylinder mowers designed for sports professionals and a variety of sports grounds including bowling greens, baseball fields, and more.</p>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al4.jpg" alt="Allett Shaver" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Shaver Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">A beautifully balanced fine-turf mower designed for cricket, bowls, and golf clubs. Provides an exceptional, precision-cut finish. The Allett Shaver is known for its precise performance and simple maintenance, making it the go-to mower for premium turf care in the sports industry.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al4.jpg" alt="Allett Tournament" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Tournament Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">Features an integral powered turf groomer to lift lateral grasses, providing a consistent level finish ideal for sports like bowls, cricket, and golf. With its specialized groomer and precision cutting, the Tournament range delivers consistent results even in the most demanding sports conditions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <img src="../images/al5.jpg" alt="Allett Buffalo" class="product-image">
            <div class="product-name">Allett Buffalo Range</div>
            <p class="product-description">The versatile all-rounder that delivers a superb finish on various grass types and conditions. Perfect for low fuel consumption and low noise operation. Designed for durability and low maintenance, the Buffalo range is ideal for larger gardens and sports fields that require consistent, professional-quality mowing.</p>
        </div>
    </section>


    <%- include('Layoutsheets/footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>
